msgid ""
"data/events_special_fleet.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"NEBULA_LIGHT_FLEET_CHAOS\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[3]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"As Vance attempts to hail the fleet, the gnome begins to screech, attempting"
" to drown out your comms. Without missing a beat, the Admiral punts the "
"gnome into the corner, causing it to shut up for now, and demands the fleet "
"let you pass."

#: src-en/data/events_special_fleet.xml.append:335
msgid ""
"data/events_special_fleet.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"NEBULA_LIGHT_FLEET_CHAOS\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[4]/text"
msgstr ""
"The gnome appears to be jamming your comms. You can't contact the fleet."

#: src-en/data/events_special_fleet.xml.append:339
msgid ""
"data/events_special_fleet.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"NEBULA_LIGHT_FLEET_CHAOS\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[5]/text"
msgstr "(Forged Identification) Try to pass your ship for a Rebel one."

#: src-en/data/events_special_fleet.xml.append:341
msgid ""
"data/events_special_fleet.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"NEBULA_LIGHT_FLEET_CHAOS\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[5]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"As you hand over your ID, the gnome screeches, transforming the data on your"
" card into a number of cognito-hazardous symbols. The Rebel slumps back, "
"their eyes completely black, leaking gallons of blood from their mouth as "
"the other horrified Rebels move into combat position!"

#: src-en/data/events_special_fleet.xml.append:343
msgid ""
"data/events_special_fleet.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"NEBULA_LIGHT_FLEET_CHAOS\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[5]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

